subsection.p:
The reciprocals (cosecant, secant and cotangent) of these functions also play important roles in trigonometry and calculus:
\csc \theta &= \frac{1}{\sin\theta} = \frac{\text{h}}{\text{o}} & \sec\theta &= \frac{1}{\cos \theta} = \frac{\text{h}}{\text{a}} & \cot\theta &= \frac{1}{\tan \theta} = \frac{\cos \theta}{\sin\theta} = \frac{\text{a}}{\text{o}}
